### Module Folder Rules

Each feature module under `src/modules/<feature>/` should own its vertical slice:

- `*.routes.ts`
- `*.controller.ts`
- `*.service.ts`
- `*.validation.ts`
- `*.types.ts`
- `*.model.ts` when persistence is module-specific
- `*.repository.ts` only when justified
- `*.constants.ts` only for module-local constants

Shared cross-module logic belongs in `src/utils/`, `src/constants/`, or a clearly named shared module — never copied.

Do not create empty folders for appearance.

